trans-unit.source: Implements a markup extension that enables <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Imaging.ColorConvertedBitmap"></xref> creation.
trans-unit.target: Implementerer filtypen markup som aktiverer <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Imaging.ColorConvertedBitmap"> </xref> oppretting.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Imaging.ColorConvertedBitmap"></xref> does not have an embedded profile, the profile instead being based on source and destination values.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Imaging.ColorConvertedBitmap"> </xref> har ikke en innebygd profil, profil i stedet blir basert på kilde- og verdier.

trans-unit.source: This class is a markup extension implementation.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen er en markup utvidelsen implementering.

trans-unit.source: Markup extension classes exist mainly to provide infrastructure support for some aspect of the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] processor implementation, and the members exposed by a markup extension are not typically called from user code.
trans-unit.target: Markup utvidelsen klassene finnes først og fremst for å gi infrastruktur støtte for deler av det [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] prosessor implementering og medlemmer vises av filtypen markup ikke kalles fra brukerkode.

trans-unit.source: This extension supports the [ColorConvertedBitmap Markup Extension](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) usage from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Denne utvidelsen støtter den [ColorConvertedBitmap Markup utvidelsen](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) Bruk fra [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: ## XAML Text Usage For [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] information, see [ColorConvertedBitmap Markup Extension](../Topic/ColorConvertedBitmap%20Markup%20Extension.md).
trans-unit.target: ## XAML tekst-Bruk For [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] informasjon, se [ColorConvertedBitmap Markup filtypen](../Topic/ColorConvertedBitmap%20Markup%20Extension.md).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.ColorConvertedBitmapExtension"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.ColorConvertedBitmapExtension"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.ColorConvertedBitmapExtension"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.ColorConvertedBitmapExtension"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: A string that is parsed to determine three [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)]: image source, source color context, and destination color context.
trans-unit.target: En streng som er analysert for å finne ut tre [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)]: bilde kilde, kilden for konteksten og målet for konteksten.

trans-unit.source: Returns an object that should be set on the property where this extension is applied.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer et objekt som skal angis for egenskapen der denne utvidelsen skal brukes.

trans-unit.source: An object that can provide services for the markup extension.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som kan gi tjenester for markup filtypen.

trans-unit.source: This service is expected to provide results for <xref:System.Windows.Markup.IUriContext>.
trans-unit.target: Denne tjenesten er forventet å oppgi resultater for <xref:System.Windows.Markup.IUriContext>.</xref:System.Windows.Markup.IUriContext>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Imaging.ColorConvertedBitmap"></xref> based on the values passed to the constructor.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Imaging.ColorConvertedBitmap"> </xref> basert på verdier som er sendt til konstruktøren.
